articles.title: Webb maps Uranus's mysterious upper atmosphere - European Space Agency
articles.description: For the first time, an international team of astronomers have mapped the vertical structure of Uranus’s upper atmosphere, uncovering how temperature and charged particles vary with height across the planet. Using NASA/ESA/CSA James Webb Space Telescope's…
